.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-LEDGER-SEARCH" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-ledger-search \- search ledger entries by note text
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-ledger-search
.I query
.RB [ --account
.IR address ]
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Performs a substring search over ledger entry notes.
Default limit is 50 results.
Returns an empty array if the wallet is not found or no entries match.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{entry_id, account_id, direction, amount_sat, note, created_at}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-export-csv (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-transaction-log (1)
